## Category

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories

### Get all categories by recipeId
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/recipe?recipeId=asdf

### Get category by id or name
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/breakfast

### Create a category
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 51cc0e81-4dcb-43f2-8a3d-ce77c99ac562

{
    "name": "Breakfast",
    "imageUrl": ""
}

### Update a category
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/a2040076-31b3-4ffc-8c4c-316e89dff17d
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 51cc0e81-4dcb-43f2-8a3d-ce77c99ac562

{
    "name": "Brunch",
    "imageUrl": ""
}

### Delete a category
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/8a04a2b3-ab6d-47e2-831d-b3cb54f57991
Authorization: Bearer 51cc0e81-4dcb-43f2-8a3d-ce77c99ac562